Details

Dataframe containing a wide variety of genome comparison calculations. Calculations ending with "..._bestpair" are meant to be utilized for bacteria, archaea, and other species with many plasmid, minichromosomes, etc. The bestpair calculation compares the two largest chromosomes of each species rather than the entire genome.

Source

Data comes from Nextflow pairwise alignment pipeline.

Examples

data(exDataFrame)
## maybe str(exDataFrame) ; plot(exDataFrame) ...
